comments: Dinwiddie (WAS) and Herro (MIA) engage and separate as both players move around the screen.
Herro (MIA) makes incidental contact as he naturally releases from Harrell (WAS) during his drive.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Dinwiddie's (WAS) path during the dribble hand-off, and incidental contact occurs.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a legal vertical position in Beal's (WAS) path and absorbs the body contact at the end of the drive.
MIA commits a 24-second shot clock violation.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal body contact with Harrell (WAS), who is already jumping toward the baseline on the rebound.
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) swipes down and makes contact with the ball at the end of Lowry's (MIA) drive.
Kuzma (WAS) turns his body and delivers contact into Adebayo (MIA), which affects his shot attempt.
Lowry (MIA) delivers his forearm into Kuzma's (WAS) body, which affects his ability to get to the inbound pass.
Beal (WAS) moves alongside Butler's (MIA) path when incidental body contact occurs on the driving shot attempt.
Herro (MIA) makes contact with the ball before brushing Dinwiddie's (WAS) leg in the backcourt.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal contact as he brushes Dinwiddie's (WAS) side on the perimeter.
Dinwiddie (WAS) gathers the ball on his right foot and establishes his left foot as his pivot before coming to a stop. He then legally lifts his pivot to pass.
Tucker (MIA) commits a take foul on Kuzma (WAS).
Herro (MIA) gathers the ball and maintains his pivot foot before passing.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Kuzma's (WAS) path during the pick.
Harrell (WAS) makes marginal body contact with Butler (MIA) as Butler is already losing control of the ball on the perimeter.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal contact with Harrell (WAS) as he naturally releases on his step-back.

After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that the foul occurred prior to the expiration of the game clock. Tucker (MIA) extends his forearm into Kuzma's (WAS) side during the rebound.
